Source: https://github.com/openclaw/openclaw/blob/main/docs/providers/index.md

This snippet demonstrates how to configure the default primary LLM model within OpenClaw's settings using JSON5 format. Ensure the 'model' property is correctly set to your desired provider and model.

```json5
{
  agents: {
    defaults: {
      model: { primary: "anthropic/claude-opus-4-5" }
    }
  }
}
```

